      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 23.7 - 老子 23.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 23.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>而況於人乎？故從事於道者，道者同於道，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore when one is making the Dao his business, those who are also pursuing it, agree with him in it, and those who are making the manifestation of its course their object agree with him in that;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-023__align-007">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-023</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 23.10 - 老子 23.12</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 23.8 - 老子 23.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>德者同於德，失者同於失。同於道者，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>while even those who are failing in both these things agree with him where they fail. Hence, those with whom he agrees as to the Dao have the happiness of attaining to it;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
