      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 23.15 - 老子 23.16</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 23.11</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>德亦樂得之；同於失者，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>and those with whom he agrees in their failure have also the happiness of attaining (to the Dao).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
