      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 23.17 - 老子 23.19</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 23.12</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>失亦樂得之。信不足焉，有不信焉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(But) when there is not faith sufficient (on his part), a want of faith (in him) ensues (on the part of the others).</seg>
      </tuv>
